# Agent execution (superDemoApp)

- **Think:** Below ~95% confidence on architecture or API → use always-applied
  `superDemoApp/AGENTS.md` (via `agents-map` rule) and relevant `superDemoApp/docs/*.md`
  before coding.
- **Change:** Smallest reversible diff; every line traces to the request or required
  lint/doc update.
- **Prove:** `./superDemoApp/bin/lint.sh` after Swift edits; `./superDemoApp/bin/ci.sh`
  before merge/PR; SwiftUI layout/navigation/universal UI/light-dark →
  `./superDemoApp/bin/checklist` (iPhone test + iPad/Mac builds).
- **Stuck:** Same failure twice → add script, test, or doc — not a longer prompt.
